casebody.data:
BOARD OF COMMISSIONERS OF the SOUTHEAST LOUISIANA FLOOD PROTECTION AUTHORITY-EAST, et al., petitioners,
v.
TENNESSEE GAS PIPELINE COMPANY, L.L.C., et al. No. 17-99. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 30, 2017.

Motion of Law Professors for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.

Justice ALITO took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
